<!-- XMP Rights Management Schema Example -->
<!-- These properties are all optional and deal with rights  -->
<!-- management.All alternations are for multiple languages. -->

<!-- Two XML packets are shown.  The first uses an expanded  -->
<!-- form similar to XMP's "pretty" format, with additional  -->
<!-- comments.  The second uses XMP's compact form, but with -->
<!-- newlines and indentation added for readability.         -->

